é Farmer]], American author (b. 1918) *[[2010]] &ndash; [[İhsan Doğramacı]], Turkish pediatrician and academic (b. 1915) *[[2011]] &ndash; [[Nikos Alexiou]], Greek painter and set designer (b. 1960) *[[2012]] &ndash; [[Lynn Compton]], American lieutenant, lawyer, and judge (b. 1921) * 2012 &ndash; [[Louisiana Red]], American singer-songwriter and guitarist (b. 1932) *[[2013]] &ndash; [[Stewart "Dirk" Fischer]], American trumpet player and composer (b. 1924) * 2013 &ndash; [[C. Everett Koop]], American surgeon and admiral, 13th [[Surgeon General of the United States]] (b. 1916) * 2013 &ndash; [[Ray O'Connor]], Australian soldier and politician, 22nd [[Premier of Western Australia]] (b. 1926) *[[2014]] &ndash; [[Angèle Arsenault]], Canadian singer-songwriter (b. 1943) * 2014 &ndash; [[Mário Coluna]], Portuguese footballer (b. 1935) * 2014 &ndash; [[Paco de Lucía]], Spanish guitarist, songwriter, and producer (b. 1947) * 2014 &ndash; [[Chokwe Lumumba]], American lawyer and politician (b. 1947) *[[2015]] &ndash; [[Harve Bennett]], American screenwriter and producer (b. 1930) * 2015 &ndash; [[Eugenie Clark]], American biologist and academic (b. 1922) *[[2017]] &ndash; [[Neil Fingleton]], English actor and basketball player, one of the tallest 25 men in the world (b. 1980) * 2017 &ndash; [[Bill Paxton]], American actor (b. 1955) <!--Do not add people without Wikipedia articles to this list. Do not trust "this year in history" websites for accurate date information. Do not link multiple occurrences of the same year, just link the first occurrence.-->
