The '''Six Days of Bremen''' is a [[Six-day racing|six-day track cycling race]] held annually in [[Bremen]], [[Germany]]. The event was first held in 1910 as a one-off event and as a regular event since 1965.<ref>http://www.memoire-du-cyclisme.eu/piste_6jours/6j_bremen.php</ref> It is held at the [[ÖVB Arena]].

